::Prowl/Kluster::

Prowl steps back as Iron Raptor steps away from him, a hurt expression 
entering into his eyes as he hears her growl, realizing she didn't want him 
to touch her. Anger began to build up in him, at himself. Why was he so 
stupid? Prowl sighs, looking at the three other bots in the room. If he had 
known that his teasing would have had this effect, he wouldn't have spoken 
back there.

He looks at the other bots, keeping quiet.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Kluster frowns, looking from Iron Raptor to Battera. As he heard it, this 
peace talk was a risky operation, with alot of chance of ambush. But it was 
the commander's decision, he'll keep his mouth shut untill she started making 
bad ones.
